2516 typedef struct CRC_MemMap {
2517  union { /* offset: 0x0 */
2518  struct { /* offset: 0x0 */
2519  uint16_t CRCL;
2520  uint16_t CRCH;
2521  } ACCESS16BIT;
2522  uint32_t CRC;
2523  struct { /* offset: 0x0 */
2524  uint8_t CRCLL;
2525  uint8_t CRCLU;
2526  uint8_t CRCHL;
2527  uint8_t CRCHU;
2528  } ACCESS8BIT;
2529  };
2530  union { /* offset: 0x4 */
2531  struct { /* offset: 0x4 */
2532  uint16_t GPOLYL;
2533  uint16_t GPOLYH;
2534  } GPOLY_ACCESS16BIT;
2535  uint32_t GPOLY;
2536  struct { /* offset: 0x4 */
2537  uint8_t GPOLYLL;
2538  uint8_t GPOLYLU;
2539  uint8_t GPOLYHL;
2540  uint8_t GPOLYHU;
2541  } GPOLY_ACCESS8BIT;
2542  };
2543  union { /* offset: 0x8 */
2544  uint32_t CTRL;
2545  struct { /* offset: 0x8 */
2546  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
2547  uint8_t CTRLHU;
2548  } CTRL_ACCESS8BIT;
2549  };
2550 } volatile *CRC_MemMapPtr;

5356 typedef struct FTM_MemMap {
5357  uint32_t SC;
5358  uint32_t CNT;
5359  uint32_t MOD;
5360  struct { /* offset: 0xC, array step: 0x8 */
5361  uint32_t CnSC;
5362  uint32_t CnV;
5363  } CONTROLS[8];
5364  uint32_t CNTIN;
5365  uint32_t STATUS;
5366  uint32_t MODE;
5367  uint32_t SYNC;
5368  uint32_t OUTINIT;
5369  uint32_t OUTMASK;
5370  uint32_t COMBINE;
5371  uint32_t DEADTIME;
5372  uint32_t EXTTRIG;
5373  uint32_t POL;
5374  uint32_t FMS;
5375  uint32_t FILTER;
5376  uint32_t FLTCTRL;
5377  uint32_t QDCTRL;
5378  uint32_t CONF;
5379  uint32_t FLTPOL;
5380  uint32_t SYNCONF;
5381  uint32_t INVCTRL;
5382  uint32_t SWOCTRL;
5383  uint32_t PWMLOAD;
5384 } volatile *FTM_MemMapPtr;

6742  uint32_t STIM_READ[32];
6743  uint32_t STIM_WRITE[32];
6744  };

6748  uint32_t TPR;

6750  uint32_t TCR;
6751  uint8_t RESERVED_3[300];
6752  uint32_t LAR;
6753  uint32_t LSR;
6754  uint8_t RESERVED_4[24];
6755  uint32_t PID4;
6756  uint32_t PID5;
6757  uint32_t PID6;
6758  uint32_t PID7;
6759  uint32_t PID0;
6760  uint32_t PID1;
6761  uint32_t PID2;
6762  uint32_t PID3;
6763  uint32_t CID0;
6764  uint32_t CID1;
6765  uint32_t CID2;
6766  uint32_t CID3;
6767 } volatile *ITM_MemMapPtr;

8486 typedef struct PDB_MemMap {
8487  uint32_t SC;
8488  uint32_t MOD;
8489  uint32_t CNT;
8490  uint32_t IDLY;
8491  struct { /* offset: 0x10, array step: 0x28 */
8492  uint32_t C1;
8493  uint32_t S;
8494  uint32_t DLY[2];
8495  uint8_t RESERVED_0[24];
8496  } CH[2];
8497  uint8_t RESERVED_0[240];
8498  struct { /* offset: 0x150, array step: 0x8 */
8499  uint32_t INTC;
8500  uint32_t INT;
8501  } DAC[1];
8502  uint8_t RESERVED_1[56];
8503  uint32_t POEN;
8504  uint32_t PODLY[3];
8505 } volatile *PDB_MemMapPtr;

12074 typedef struct USB_MemMap {
12075  uint8_t PERID;
12076  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
12077  uint8_t IDCOMP;
12078  uint8_t RESERVED_1[3];
12079  uint8_t REV;
12080  uint8_t RESERVED_2[3];
12081  uint8_t ADDINFO;
12082  uint8_t RESERVED_3[3];
12083  uint8_t OTGISTAT;
12084  uint8_t RESERVED_4[3];
12085  uint8_t OTGICR;
12086  uint8_t RESERVED_5[3];
12087  uint8_t OTGSTAT;
12088  uint8_t RESERVED_6[3];
12089  uint8_t OTGCTL;
12090  uint8_t RESERVED_7[99];
12091  uint8_t ISTAT;
12092  uint8_t RESERVED_8[3];
12093  uint8_t INTEN;
12094  uint8_t RESERVED_9[3];
12095  uint8_t ERRSTAT;
12096  uint8_t RESERVED_10[3];
12097  uint8_t ERREN;
12098  uint8_t RESERVED_11[3];
12099  uint8_t STAT;
12100  uint8_t RESERVED_12[3];
12101  uint8_t CTL;
12102  uint8_t RESERVED_13[3];
12103  uint8_t ADDR;
12104  uint8_t RESERVED_14[3];
12105  uint8_t BDTPAGE1;
12106  uint8_t RESERVED_15[3];
12107  uint8_t FRMNUML;
12108  uint8_t RESERVED_16[3];
12109  uint8_t FRMNUMH;
12110  uint8_t RESERVED_17[3];
12111  uint8_t TOKEN;
12112  uint8_t RESERVED_18[3];
12113  uint8_t SOFTHLD;
12114  uint8_t RESERVED_19[3];

12116  uint8_t RESERVED_20[3];
12117  uint8_t BDTPAGE3;
